          "value": "Energy transition investor and industrial strategist who builds long-term infrastructure platforms across grid modernization, regulated utilities, and energy transition. Founded Helios Ridge Capital and chairs Northshore Energy Systems, after earlier operating roles and a board seat at Prosek Partners. Recognized with the Energy Infrastructure Leadership Award and active in climate philanthropy through the Laurent Foundation."
